{"tid":998950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔洗再報到 好唔慣 可唔可以快啲過","createTime":"2019-01-28T10:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T16:14:20.000Z","uid":56375,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"316e9b1b3190ded18a91ad0ccbc123e5e2ca1aa6","tid":998950,"uid":56375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"一年了，<br />\n一年入面無論咩身份關係，都係大小事乜都傾。<br />\n返工會同你講，食lunch會同你講，放工會同你講...直至琴日，大家講出口嗰一刻，所有野都唔同了。<br />\n<br />\n唔會再報到，唔會再搵你傾計，無聊個時唔係諗約你去邊，而係諗之前一齊嘅畫面，好唔習慣。好灰，好想叫，好想大叫。<br />\n<br />\n點解要偏偏喺我差唔多放假先同我講，點解？我知所有野都返唔到轉頭，我只係想依段時間快啲過。我冇嬲過你冇怪過你，我只係好憎我自己。<br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到嘅，我唔係特登打出黎畀你睇，我只係想搵個地方發洩。琴晚我冇乜情緒冇乜反應只係因為我真係好唔開心，我知依日遲早都會出現，只係冇諗到快到連我地約好嘅日子都過唔到。"},{"pid":"059ce22ba0d36cbe6b47b431a2dd22f44379d55d","tid":998950,"uid":33483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"小學生寫日記呀？"},{"pid":"350a2a19b7bcf0002f991e1d891d6d94dcf7433b","tid":998950,"uid":56375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:58:07.000Z","msg":"感情台唔啱你"},{"pid":"c759db5a20731be40e144849b738998806ddeccd","tid":998950,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:59:07.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"b9d5ae8739024ff60c017d920825b95f15bb8625","tid":998950,"uid":7988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"點解我會追蹤左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8823e986d605e03b6cdf8077b24532fc6ee9bb24","tid":998950,"uid":56375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9d5ae8739024ff60c017d920825b95f15bb8625","tid":998950,"uid":7988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"點解我會追蹤左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b3dd119cdc95d79e1ca25d225b7c997238346f